fields.address_string: 217 E Houston St, New York, NY 10002

fields.title: Pianos
fields.description: Pianos is a two-story bar/restaurant/live music venue in the Lower East Side section of Manhattan at 158 Ludlow Street. Its stage attracts local and national alternative rock groups as well as DJs, though a more typical performance consists of smaller name local and touring acts.

fields.title: FM Bar
fields.description:
Showcasing local bands, DJs and Art groups, FM is a celebration of the music scene that makes up the fabric of Jersey City and the surrounding area.

Relaunched in the winter of 2018, FM's new shift focuses on bringing together up and coming local arts in a casual setting with good vibes.

Come in for a drink, food, stay for a show and enjoy some of the best Jersey City has to offer.

We hope to see you soon!
